    "longBusinessSummary": "Tien Giang Investment and Construction Joint Stock Company engages in manufacturing and trading of fresh and precast concrete products in Vietnam. It also constructs irrigation works, civil and industrial works, traffic bridges, wharves, roads, and water supply and drainage systems, as well as invests in and constructs industrial parks and residential areas. In addition, the company is involved in site leveling; designing and surveying of traffic and irrigation works; bidding and supervision consultancy activities; trading of sand for leveling; and repairing of barges and equipment. Further, it engages in the wholesale of equipment and supplies; treating and coating of metals; and trading and wholesale of construction materials, as well as processes mechanical products and sluice gates for irrigation works. Additionally, the company offers real estate brokerage, valuation, consulting, advertising, auction, and management services; and transport exploitation services. The company was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in My Tho, Vietnam.",
